        "description": {
          "value": "<p class=\"feature\">Tamsin has spent twelve years grading and contracting harvest sales for Aerdi-coastal buyers. She can examine any grain shipment record, insurance claim, or bonded-factor ledger and identify discrepancies automatically — no roll required for documents she has time to study. When rolling Investigation or Nature to assess trade documents, harvest records, or false-crop schemes, she has Advantage and treats a result below 12 as a 12.</p>",
